{
  "texts": [
    "As this includes both procedural and outcomebased features this approach naturally combines the two.",
    "It also closely mirrors the development process, at least in ideal cases.",
    "AI systems should be developed in accordance with the values of the different stakeholders that are impacted by them.",
    "To ensure that this happens we need a systematic approach to the inclusion of these values.",
    "In that sense, the transparency requirement here asks for no more than that organizations that develop and implement AI show how they have incorporated (ethical) values during the development of the (socio-)technical system and that they report how successful this was."
  ]
}